    Am J Clin Nutr
    Effect of calorie restriction in comparison to usual diet or usual care on remission of type 2 diabetes: a systematic review and meta-analysis of randomized controlled trials.
Calorie-restricted diets may be effective interventions for type 2 diabetes remission, especially when coupled with an intensive lifestyle modification program. Systematic review registration PROSPERO (CRD42022300875).
